, <a href="/web/20180712184637/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_MTH_CUI=C0375111&amp;fLockTerm=Neoplasm+of+unspecified+nature%2c+site+unspecified">Neoplasm of unspecified nature, site unspecified</a>
, <a href="/web/20180712184637/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_MTH_CUI=C0027651&amp;fLockTerm=Neoplasms">Neoplasms</a>
, <a href="/web/20180712184637/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_MTH_CUI=C0030688&amp;fLockTerm=Patient+education+(procedure)">Patient education (procedure)</a>
, <a href="/web/20180712184637/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_MTH_CUI=C1718917&amp;fLockTerm=Patient+Health+Questionnaire+PHQ-9+administration">Patient Health Questionnaire PHQ-9 administration</a>
